document.full_text: champion rafael nadal was forced to pull out all the stops and leave john isner battling for "oxygen" in a 6-4 6-7 6-7 6-2 6-4 win in the french open first round tuesday, his first five-set match at roland garros.
document.title: nadal digs deep to beat giant isner in five sets
